                <section id="fes-team-page"><div class="wrap"><div class="intro"><h1><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Our Team</span></strong></h1><br><h2>We Know the Industry Because We&rsquo;re From the Industry</h2><p>This platform wasn&rsquo;t built by tech investors, it was built by people who&rsquo;ve been in the industry for decades. We understand what it takes to move iron and how frustrating the overpriced listing platforms can be. We&rsquo;re lean, efficient, and focused on one goal: helping you sell and buy logging equipment faster and easier.</p></div><div class="team-grid"><div class="team-card"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/aqa9zbltl/images/1b63bbd7f47bcd5731c901a5ad68fa48393c8482.webp" alt="Aaron Blake" class="team-photo fr-fic fr-dii"><h3>Aaron Blake</h3><p class="role"><span style="color: rgb(17, 46, 78);">Co-Owner &amp; Sales</span></p><p>With more than 22 years of experience in logging and equipment sales, Aaron has built a reputation as someone you can trust &amp; knows how to get deals done. He manages risk, supports all sales, and helps clients secure financing to close deals.</p></div><div class="team-card"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/aqa9zbltl/images/2b41123220474453445f2a2e50123f64cafd5d0b.jpg" alt="Erik Madsen" class="team-photo fr-fic fr-dii"><h3>Erik Madsen</h3><p class="role"><span style="color: rgb(17, 46, 78);">Co-Owner &amp; Sales</span></p><p>Erik brings sharp instincts and hands-on knowledge of equipment. He helps sellers move their machines efficiently, supports financing efforts, and uses his industry knowledge to drive results-oriented deals.</p></div><div class="team-card"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/aqa9zbltl/images/9d11f5ae877b93e2968e86026c9558ab7e740108.jpg" alt="Kelly Brooks" class="team-photo fr-fic fr-dii"><h3>Kelly Brooks</h3><p class="role"><span style="color: rgb(17, 46, 78);">Front Office &amp; Logistics</span></p><p>Kelly keeps our front office running like a machine. She handles phones, logistics, customs, overseas shipping, customer support, and website updates to make sure everything stays organized and efficient.</p></div><div class="team-card"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/aqa9zbltl/images/675a11d33eca36acc1fa34fa96075f11c1302b2a.jpg" alt="Caleb Happy" class="team-photo fr-fic fr-dii"><h3>Caleb Happy</h3><p class="role"><span style="color: rgb(17, 46, 78);">Marketing &amp; Platform Development</span></p><p>Caleb brings eight years of marketing experience and a hands-on systems knowledge. He handles marketing, infrastructure, and customer relations to keep the platform running smoothly.</p></div></div><div class="promise-card fes-card"><h3>Our Pledge</h3><p>We answer the phone. We respond to emails. And we do everything we can to help contractors and equipment dealers move machines faster - without the BS. This platform is built on hard work, relationships, and respect for the industry we serve.</p></div><div class="final-cta fes-card"><h3>Get in Touch</h3><p>Questions, feedback, or partnership ideas?</p><a class="btn" href="/about/contact">Contact Us</a></div></div></section>        </div>

        
